e":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"覺得生存好痛苦 好想逃避"},{"pid":"58caba9ade2c01587c48003028bd4584b1842c67","tid":1818262,"uid":140956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"11 月係咁<br />\n日日搵人傾之後冇事"},{"pid":"e51ccafddc17be737fa20b65f421b78c2d86c1ef","tid":1818262,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55cad48db9a010f39493e91a65766cc3aaab397","tid":1818262,"uid":326777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"差唔多每晚都喊 <br />\n一直努力撐住叫自己堅強啲但都做唔到<br />\n有冇咩辦法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"&quot;你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=470a90a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"1b3a96415f35e78636d8e7985c301e0f7855f8e1","tid":1818262,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"日日喊 已睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291b1660ac0bcbdf39bdb5a1706f88a4a6c96db3","tid":1818262,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人一有咩發脾氣嗰啲又嚟啦 仲要佢係成日都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗壓力低都搞到我有拖延症 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90144351cad4339f458e02d26f2c4c3f51a3539f","tid":1818262,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db055ea6f138447ab563ce0f4ea305fd0748889